content: Small business owners who have been in business for years don't see investments for them in democratic platform.
It might be worth mentioning to them that VP Harris just recently announced her Entrepreneurs and Innovators policy plan!

Under Biden-Harris we also saw 19 million new business applications (Harris has already set a goal for her administration to see 25 million in her four year term), and 70% of new jobs in the US since 2019 have been created by small businesses.
